  <brief_title>Influence of Whole Body Vibration Compared to Conventional Physiotherapy in Patients With Gonarthrosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>Influence of Whole Body Vibration Compared to Conventional Physiotherapy in Patients With Gonarthrosis</official_title>
